    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 11,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Beidou_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "北斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "北斗在隊伍中如果擔當後臺雷屬性副C，則會比較需要提高元素爆發的覆蓋率。該武器在祭禮系列中白值較高，副詞綴也能提高北斗的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，武器特效能讓北斗連續釋放兩次倍率可觀的元素戰技，是比較適合副C北斗的武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "辛焱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器之於辛焱猶如祭禮弓之於迪奧娜，能增加辛焱護盾的覆蓋率，變相提供了更大覆蓋率的物理傷害加成。但辛焱護盾的能力是基於防禦力的，同時沒有迪奧娜長按帶來的的吸收量加成，需要仔細斟酌是否培養使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
